e>連埋交通返12個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n訓八個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  得返四個鐘沖涼食飯做自己野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以點解唔考慮訓六個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c95919432fe60a1e4a326744f6ea4144c634f5","tid":273480,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:12:35.000Z","msg":"以前返個份工工時連ot連搭車可以超過14個鐘 一星期連食飯返超過60個鐘<br />\n個陣既生活係起身返工 收工返屋企訓 起身又返工 不停loop 人工又唔係高<br />\n<br />\n而家轉左文職 人工高啲 一星期返5日 一星期先44個鐘 準時收工 ot會補返鐘 有返好多自己時間<br />\n可以去上自己想上既堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f1c57d8d53392d1d6b15611f1516c89148892e","tid":273480,"uid":22048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:12:55.000Z","msg":"仲要返6日全日<br />\n得返一日假又好想係屋企hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似冇晒自己生活咁<br />\n<br />\n睇住d fd係外國working holiday<br />\n一日8個鐘ot有1.5甚至2倍人工 一星期最多返4日<br />\n再睇下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想轉5天工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97115483f1248664d36d3c418604d4b295436191","tid":273480,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:16:08.000Z","msg":"試過1000-2600/2800咁返足一個月<br />\n晚晚返到屋企屋企人訓晒教<br />\n一返到去就沖涼吹頭訓<br />\n<br />\n而家朝9晚6，一搭正就閃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4799e59fb6e33524f287e019f5dd793a8c16a84b","tid":273480,"uid":11911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:17:23.000Z","msg":"我14<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未計交通<br />\n不過pt黎"},{"pid":"49b5150dcf424fc953d7cda20863bcd9a6e429b8","tid":273480,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re